## ğŸ“Š Summary Table

| Adder Type         | Speed       | Area       | Power   | Typical Use |
|--------------------|------------|------------|---------|-------------|
| Ripple Carry (RCA) | Slow       | Low        | Low     | Simple ALUs |
| Carry Lookahead    | Fast       | High       | High    | High-speed CPUs |
| Carry Select       | Medium-Fast| Medium-High| Medium  | Microcontrollers |
| Adder-Subtractor   | Medium     | Medium     | Medium  | ALUs, DSPs |

